# 2. Patient Registration Module

## Purpose
Register patient and family into membership ecosystem.

## Pages

- Patient registration form
- Family member form
- Document upload page
- Plan selection page
- Consent form
- Card generation page

## Inputs

- Name
- Mobile
- DOB
- Gender
- Address
- Area
- Email
- KYC documents
- Consent
- Family member details
- Membership plan

## Outputs

- Patient profile
- Family member profiles
- Membership record
- Health card number
- QR code
- PDF card
- WhatsApp share status
- Registration logs

## API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint |
|--------|----------|
| POST | /patients/register |
| POST | /patients/family-member |
| POST | /patients/documents |
| POST | /patients/consent |
| POST | /cards/generate |
| GET | /cards/:id/pdf |
| POST | /cards/:id/share |

## Validation Rules

- Unique mobile number
- Duplicate detection
- Mandatory fields
